00:56:37.143 --> 00:56:39.354 line:85.83%,end
Hey. Dream on.

00:56:40.772 --> 00:56:41.689 line:85.83%,end
Bun-ok.

00:56:44.943 --> 00:56:46.111 line:85.83%,end
Go bring some water.

00:56:47.779 --> 00:56:48.863 line:85.83%,end
Hot water.

00:56:55.161 --> 00:56:56.162 line:85.83%,end
You.

00:56:57.497 --> 00:56:58.915 line:85.83%,end
Stay put.

00:57:00.834 --> 00:57:02.544 line:85.83%,end
