01:00:30.376 --> 01:00:32.128 line:85.83%,end
I'm so sorry.

01:00:34.881 --> 01:00:37.008 line:85.83%,end
Sang-beom.

01:00:37.091 --> 01:00:39.052 line:85.83%,end
